                "value": "Hello locale 'en-US': In European languages we have some characters that may seem special to you but which are normal to us: It turns out that this APL will crash when String.slice() reaches one of the the letters äöü"
              }
            ],
            "text": "${String.slice(textToAutoscroll,Time.milliseconds(localTime/100)%(218))}",
            "fontSize": "10dp",
            "position": "absolute",
            "top": "45vh"
          }
        ],
        "height": "100%",
        "width": "100%"
      }
    ]
  }
